---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Help Center - DigitalStoreTrujillo">
    <Header />
    <div class="min-h-screen bg-background-dark py-12 px-4 lg:px-40">
        <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Help Center</h1>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
                <!-- FAQ Section -->
                <div
                    class="bg-surface-dark border border-border-dark rounded-lg p-6"
                >
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                        <span
                            class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl"
                            >help</span
                        >
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">
                            Frequently Asked Questions
                        </h2>
                    </div>

                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <details class="group">
                            <summary
                                class="cursor-pointer text-white font-semibold py-2 hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                            >
                                How do I receive my digital products?
                            </summary>
                            <p class="text-text-muted text-sm mt-2 pl-4">
                                After completing your purchase, you will receive
                                an email with download links and activation keys
                                (if applicable). You can also access your
                                purchases from your account dashboard.
                            </p>
                        </details>

                        <details class="group">
                            <summary
                                class="cursor-pointer text-white font-semibold py-2 hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                            >
                                What payment methods do you accept?
                            </summary>
                            <p class="text-text-muted text-sm mt-2 pl-4">
                                We accept cryptocurrency payments (Bitcoin,
                                USDT, etc.) through Cryptomus, as well as local
                                payment methods like Yape and Binance Pay.
                            </p>
                        </details>

                        <details class="group">
                            <summary
                                class="cursor-pointer text-white font-semibold py-2 hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                            >
                                How long does delivery take?
                            </summary>
                            <p class="text-text-muted text-sm mt-2 pl-4">
                                Digital products are delivered instantly after
                                payment confirmation. You'll receive your access
                                within minutes.
                            </p>
                        </details>

                        <details class="group">
                            <summary
                                class="cursor-pointer text-white font-semibold py-2 hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                            >
                                ¿De dónde provienen mis claves?
                            </summary>
                            <p class="text-text-muted text-sm mt-2 pl-4">
                                DigitalStoreTrujillo obtiene sus claves y
                                servicios digitales de tres fuentes principales:
                                (1) programa de afiliados G2A Goldmine (G2A
                                Marketplace); (2) programa de afiliados de
                                Eneba; y (3) compras directas en la plataforma
                                de comparación de precios Keysforgames. No
                                generamos claves por nuestra cuenta ni
                                utilizamos métodos ilícitos; solo trabajamos con
                                marketplaces reconocidos.
                            </p>
                        </details>

                        <details class="group">
                            <summary
                                class="cursor-pointer text-white font-semibold py-2 hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                            >
                                ¿Cómo se entregan los productos?
                            </summary>
                            <p class="text-text-muted text-sm mt-2 pl-4">
                                La entrega es 100% digital. Después de confirmar
                                tu pago, recibirás tus claves o credenciales por
                                correo electrónico o en tu panel de cuenta. El
                                tiempo estimado de entrega es inmediato
                                (minutos). Si experimentas algún problema con tu
                                producto, contáctanos dentro de las 24-48 horas
                                y te ayudaremos a resolverlo.
                            </p>
                        </details>

                        <details class="group">
                            <summary
                                class="cursor-pointer text-white font-semibold py-2 hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                            >
                                ¿Qué garantía tienen los productos?
                            </summary>
                            <p class="text-text-muted text-sm mt-2 pl-4">
                                Todos nuestros productos son verificados antes
                                de la entrega. Ofrecemos soporte completo
                                durante las primeras 24-48 horas después de la
                                compra. Si una clave no funciona o hay algún
                                problema técnico, la reemplazaremos sin costo
                                adicional. Probamos cada clave antes de
                                entregarla al cliente final.
                            </p>
                        </details>

                        <details class="group">
                            <summary
                                class="cursor-pointer text-white font-semibold py-2 hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                            >
                                Can I get a refund?
                            </summary>
                            <p class="text-text-muted text-sm mt-2 pl-4">
                                Please refer to our <a
                                    href="/refund-policy"
                                    class="text-primary hover:underline"
                                    >Refund Policy</a
                                > for detailed information about refunds and returns.
                            </p>
                        </details>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Contact Support -->
                <div
                    class="bg-surface-dark border border-border-dark rounded-lg p-6"
                >
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                        <span
                            class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl"
                            >support_agent</span
                        >
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">
                            Contact Support
                        </h2>
                    </div>

                    <p class="text-text-muted mb-6">
                        Can't find what you're looking for? Our support team is
                        here to help!
                    </p>

                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <a
                            href="mailto:support@digitalstoretrujillo.store"
                            class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-background-dark border border-border-dark rounded-lg hover:border-primary transition-colors"
                        >
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary"
                                >mail</span
                            >
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-white font-semibold">
                                    Email Support
                                </h3>
                                <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">
                                    support@digitalstoretrujillo.store
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </a>

                        <a
                            href="https://wa.me/51931387898"
                            target="_blank"
                            class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-background-dark border border-border-dark rounded-lg hover:border-primary transition-colors"
                        >
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary"
                                >chat</span
                            >
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-white font-semibold">
                                    WhatsApp
                                </h3>
                                <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">
                                    +51 931 387 898
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </a>

                        <a
                            href="https://t.me/netflixaccglobal"
                            target="_blank"
                            class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-background-dark border border-border-dark rounded-lg hover:border-primary transition-colors"
                        >
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary"
                                >send</span
                            >
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-white font-semibold">
                                    Telegram
                                </h3>
                                <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">
                                    @netflixaccglobal
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Popular Topics -->
            <div
                class="bg-surface-dark border border-border-dark rounded-lg p-6"
            >
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
                    Popular Topics
                </h2>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                    <a
                        href="#"
                        class="p-4 bg-background-dark border border-border-dark rounded-lg hover:border-primary transition-colors"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl mb-2"
                            >download</span
                        >
                        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-1">
                            Download Issues
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">
                            Troubleshoot download problems
                        </p>
                    </a>

                    <a
                        href="#"
                        class="p-4 bg-background-dark border border-border-dark rounded-lg hover:border-primary transition-colors"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl mb-2"
                            >key</span
                        >
                        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-1">
                            Activation Keys
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">
                            How to activate your products
                        </p>
                    </a>

                    <a
                        href="#"
                        class="p-4 bg-background-dark border border-border-dark rounded-lg hover:border-primary transition-colors"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl mb-2"
                            >account_circle</span
                        >
                        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-1">
                            Account Management
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">
                            Manage your account settings
                        </p>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <Footer />
</Layout>
